176
00:09:46.319 --> 00:09:48.803
This Marcus Cole...
Is a little politician.

177
00:09:48.872 --> 00:09:52.840
But he'd rather blame
the school than himself.
and I can work with that.

178
00:09:52.909 --> 00:09:55.743
MARCUS: <i>When you're
marginalized. powerless.</i>

179
00:09:55.812 --> 00:09:57.692
