191
00:10:28.779 --> 00:10:31.513
Look. he's at my house.
We're taking care of him.

192
00:10:31.581 --> 00:10:34.382
If you want to see him or...
I don't.

193
00:10:34.451 --> 00:10:36.718
Soon as he's better.
gonna take him
to the Bakers' lawyer.

194
00:10:36.787 --> 00:10:39.403
He can back up Hannah's story.
It's not Hannah's story.

195
00:10:39.472 --> 00:10:41.512
and it's not his story.
it's mine.

196
00:10:42.242 --> 00:10:43.875
I don't want him telling it.

197
00:10:43.944 --> 00:10:45.442
Jess. listen. Listen to me.

198
00:10:45.511 --> 00:10:47.879
Justin wants to help.
(WHISPERS) Shut up. Clay.

199
00:10:47.947 --> 00:10:50.882
ZACH: I'm just worried
about it. All right?

200
00:10:50.950 --> 00:10:52.928
I'm serious. dude.
No. I'm not kidding.

201
00:10:52.952 --> 00:10:55.252
Ask your boyfriend
for help with history.

202
00:10:55.321 --> 00:10:57.621
Oh. wait.
He's brain damaged.

203
00:10:57.691 --> 00:11:00.169
You're just jealous
he had a brain
to damage. Monty.

204
00:11:00.193 --> 00:11:03.005
Guys. if I don't ace
this test. I might
drop below a C. okay?

205
00:11:03.029 --> 00:11:06.130
So play the dad card again.
Metcalf will let you slide.

206
00:11:06.199 --> 00:11:08.566
It's not a card. dude.

207
00:11:08.634 --> 00:11:12.070
No. I know.
Fuck. sorry. brother.
You know what I mean.

208
00:11:12.138 --> 00:11:14.416
If Chloe hadn't stopped
doing study group...

209
00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:17.474
I'm sorry. Zach.
I've just been
so busy with everything.

210
00:11:17.543 --> 00:11:20.712
Yeah. "everything."
meaning doing Bryce.
(HISSING)

211
00:11:20.780 --> 00:11:22.246
Hey. well. it's Zach's fault.

212
00:11:22.315 --> 00:11:23.826
He set us up.
Yeah.

213
00:11:23.850 --> 00:11:27.384
I gave him your number.
The rest of it
isn't my fault.

214
00:11:27.453 --> 00:11:30.505
Meaning what. exactly?
Meaning I have
to get to class.

215
00:11:33.709 --> 00:11:35.154
What's going on there. Walker?

216
00:11:35.178 --> 00:11:38.112
He's just got
a lot on his mind.
I don't blame him.

217
00:11:38.181 --> 00:11:41.182
<i>(FREEZE ME</i> PLAYING)

218
00:11:42.619 --> 00:11:46.154
<i>♪ Tell me what you think.
are we in trouble?</i>

219
00:11:46.222 --> 00:11:49.890
<i>♪ Feelin' sorry's</i>
<i>never really</i>
<i>been my struggle</i>

220
00:11:49.959 --> 00:11:51.325
<i>♪ Pickin' up the pieces</i>

221
00:11:51.394 --> 00:11:53.894
<i>♪ Siftin' through
the rubble... ♪</i>

222
00:11:53.963 --> 00:11:55.729
MARCUS:
<i>When you feel left out.</i>

223
00:11:55.798 --> 00:11:58.633
<i>when you feel like</i>
<i>this high school world</i>
<i>is against you.</i>

224
00:11:58.701 --> 00:12:01.402
<i>it can be
lonely and frightening.</i>

225
00:12:01.471 --> 00:12:04.455
<i>I wouldn't want anyone
to feel that way.</i>

226
00:12:04.507 --> 00:12:06.668
Which is why I signed up
for Dollar Valentines.

227
00:12:06.692 --> 00:12:09.627
and why I invited Hannah out.

228
00:12:09.696 --> 00:12:12.376
And was there
a reason you chose
Hannah in particular?

229
00:12:13.983 --> 00:12:17.018
I knew that she'd had
some tough times at school.

230
00:12:17.820 --> 00:12:19.787
It was her first year.

231
00:12:19.856 --> 00:12:22.985
I wanted to show her
that there were
